- Use kebab-case for all file names
- Keep names lowercase
- Separate words with hyphens

GOOD:
- feature-card.html
- pricing-section.html
- navigation-menu.js
- testimonial-slider.js
- globals.css

BAD:
- FeatureCard.html
- pricingSection.html
