- card-featured
- section-dark
- badge-success

UTILITY CLASSES:
- Use only for true utilities

GOOD:
- text-balance
- section-spacing
- container-wide

==================================================
JAVASCRIPT NAMING
==================================================

VARIABLES:
- Use camelCase
- Use descriptive names

GOOD:
- mobileMenu
- activeAccordion
- currentSlide
- pricingCards

BAD:
- data
- item1
- temp
- box

FUNCTIONS:
- Use verb-first naming

GOOD:
- initializeSlider()
- toggleAccordion()
- loadComponent()
- updateNavigation()

BAD:
- slider()
- handle()
- stuff()

BOOLEAN VARIABLES:
- Prefix with:
  is
  has
  should
  can

GOOD:
- isMenuOpen
- hasScrolled
- shouldAnimate

BAD:
- menuOpen
- scrolled

EVENT HANDLERS:
- Prefix with:
  handle

GOOD:
- handleMenuToggle
- handleAccordionClick
- handleScrollAnimation

CONSTANTS:
- Use UPPER_SNAKE_CASE

GOOD:
- MOBILE_BREAKPOINT
- ANIMATION_DURATION
- MAX_SLIDES

