==================================================
AVOID THESE PATTERNS
==================================================

DO NOT:
- use appearance-based names
- use random abbreviations
- use vague wrappers
- use numbered components
- use temporary naming
- mix casing styles
- create inconsistent naming systems

AVOID:
- box
- wrapper
- container2
- temp
- final
- new-section
- purple-card

==================================================
NAMING PHILOSOPHY
==================================================

Names should describe:
- purpose
- responsibility
- behavior
- hierarchy

NOT:
- colors
- positioning
- temporary ideas
- visual appearance